result.title: The Why - Demystifying AI
result.description: WHY should your company strive to become data and AI-driven? To answer this, we must go beyond the buzz. Learn the fundamentals and core concepts behind the AI-buzz. And understand the key role you have to create real value from AI.

result.title: The How - Managing AI transformations
result.description: HOW can companies  become data- and AI-driven and how you can contribute to it? Learn the importance of establishing urgency, empower key people, and build AI initiatives on your companies unique strengths.

result.title: The What - New opportunities from AI
result.description: WHAT can you do to accelerate your company's AI transformation? Learn how you and your domain expertise are the keys to unlock new opportunities with data & AI. To prove it, we'll help you develop your own innovative AI-driven use-case idea.
